<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>Lighthouse</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Summary</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">The<sp/>``lighthouse``<sp/>plugin<sp/>supports<sp/>lighthouse<sp/>tracking<sp/>using<sp/>the<sp/>[libsurvive<sp/>library](https://github.com/collabora/libsurvive).<sp/>To<sp/>use<sp/>this<sp/>plugin,<sp/>libsurvive<sp/>should<sp/>first<sp/>be<sp/>built,<sp/>installed,<sp/>and<sp/>calibrated<sp/>according<sp/>to<sp/>[their<sp/>documentation](https://github.com/collabora/libsurvive/blob/master/README.md).<sp/>Running<sp/>ILLIXR&apos;s<sp/>CMake<sp/>to<sp/>build<sp/>the<sp/>``lighthouse``<sp/>plugin<sp/>should<sp/>automatically<sp/>build<sp/>and<sp/>install<sp/>``libsurvive``,<sp/>but<sp/>the<sp/>steps<sp/>to<sp/>calibrate<sp/>the<sp/>lighthouses<sp/>should<sp/>still<sp/>be<sp/>followed.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Note</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">If<sp/>the<sp/>``lighthouse``<sp/>plugin<sp/>is<sp/>being<sp/>used,<sp/>make<sp/>sure<sp/>to<sp/>set<sp/>the<sp/>environment<sp/>variable<sp/>``ILLIXR_LIGHTHOUSE``<sp/>to<sp/>true,<sp/>as<sp/>the<sp/>``pose_prediction``<sp/>relies<sp/>on<sp/>it.</highlight></codeline>
    </programlisting>
